commit.message: Raise Invalid_arg instead of returning a negative integer on error
Executable size: save a few bytes
Enhance vowels with diacritics (thanks to a2line)
Added a dummy cli tool to test the lib
opam: mark dune as a non-build dependency
Added benchmarks to compare with ubase library
Added tests for french and vietnamese input.
Support for vietnamese + some fixes. Work done by Henri Gouraud.
decode_string: take a function for unsupported chars instead of a replacement char
Avoid passing unnecessary arguments in decode callbacks.
Fixed wrong length for some cyrillic characters
Fixed type (call 'unsupport' on some chars instead of returning unit)
callback now take next char index as first parameter
